  "comment": " Hyaden Moving Bar with 7 LED and 8 Laser beams: The Hyaden Moving Bar is a dynamic lighting fixture that combines 7 powerful Fat LED Beams with 8 intense laser beams for a mesmerising visual experience. This space-filling light effect is ideal for clubs, events, and stages and guarantees spectacular RGBW light effects and precise laser projections. The DMX control allows for seamless customization, while the robust design ensures durability and reliability in any environment. The Hyaden is perfect for creating high-energy atmospheres and offers a versatile solution for DJs, cafés/nightclubs, and other lighting professionals looking to enhance their light shows.",
